    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The amazing chapel cum assembly hall will give a different vibe everytime you enter there.",
          "name": "Pratham Kumar Kherajani",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The study was also well mannered and attendance method too",
          "name": "Tanishka Baghel",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Also the special facility for girls with wcr room in which only girls are allowed to take rest for any emergency",
          "name": "Tanishka Baghel",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked the fests and the function conducted by our college and we gave somethingi.e. our talent to participate",
          "name": "Tanishka Baghel",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Availablity of all kind of sports and sports equipments",
          "name": "Aman Masih",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty members are nice and approachable",
          "name": "Aman Masih",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure is awesome and grounds are good",
          "name": "Aman Masih",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Labs are good for practicals all instruments are working and all required materials are available",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers are very supportive for both sports and studies",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure is amezing , opportunity for all types of sports e.g. cricket, football basketball, swimming chess",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The cricket ground staff don't allow to play cricket unless if u are with teacher",
          "name": "Harsh yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The computer science classes are very early in the morning and afterwards you reach there sometimes teacher don't come.",
          "name": "Harsh yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure of the college is too bad. The chairs and table are very old and not proper. The ceilings are very up high so the fans don't work properly either.",
          "name": "Pratham Kumar Kherajani",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are not much campus placements and opportunities for students graduated in B.Com course.",
          "name": "Pratham Kumar Kherajani",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "As far as B.Com course is concerned, the college is not so serious about the academics and so are the faculties.",
          "name": "Pratham Kumar Kherajani",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Parking is not free for students have to pay accordingly",
          "name": "Aman Masih",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Wifi is not available on all classes expect few",
          "name": "Aman Masih",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "During summer some classes have ventilation issues",
          "name": "Aman Masih",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "In library there are not many books to study",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Wi-fi is not available in all classes and sometimes it's slow",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ]
    },
